NullBool.description:
Bool is a nullable bool.
It does not consider false values to be null.
It will decode to null, not false, if null.
NullBool.title: NullBool

NullFloat.description:
Float is a nullable float64.
It does not consider zero values to be null.
It will decode to null, not zero, if null.
NullFloat.title: NullFloat

NullInt.description:
Int is an nullable int64.
It does not consider zero values to be null.
It will decode to null, not zero, if null.
NullInt.title: NullInt

NullString.description:
String is a nullable string. It supports SQL and JSON serialization.
It will marshal to null if null. Blank string input will be considered null.
NullString.title: NullString

String.description:
String is a nullable string. It supports SQL and JSON serialization.
It will marshal to null if null. Blank string input will be considered null.
String.title: NullString
